<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n03005b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03005b">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03005b"> 5(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Shealing hymn</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"> The people of the Hebrides invoke <font color="green">[St. Columcille&apos;s]</font> aid to this day in their annual <mark>Shealing Hymn</mark>, and the stone flag on which he was born at Gartan is worn bare by the hands and feet of pious pilgrims. <small> J.M. Flood, <a name="JMFI" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#JMFI"><cite title="source">Ireland: Its Saints and Scholars</cite></a> (n.d) 29</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
